---
import { ArrowUpRight } from "lucide-react";

import Logo from "./vectors/logo.astro";
---

<section class="h-full w-full" id="about">
  <div class="flex flex-col-reverse justify-center md:flex-row xl:px-40">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:w-1/2">
      <picture>
        <source srcset="/one-way.png" media="(min-width: 768px)" />
        <img
          src="/one-way-responsive.png"
          alt="One Way Sign"
          class="mask-gradient mt-2"
        />
      </picture>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center py-14 md:my-20 md:w-1/2">
      <div class="max-w-md">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-center text-xl md:text-left md:text-lg">
          <Logo class="mx-auto size-[250px] md:size-[150px]" />
          <span class="mt-6 font-bold">Digital Creator</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-2 text-center text-sm md:text-left">
          Somos una comunidad que vibra con las dinámicas sociales, mejor
          conocidas en República Dominicana como coro o chercha. Aquí se trata
          de pasarla bien, compartir entre panas y desbordar el carisma
          dominicano en todo su esplendor. ¡La diversión y la buena vibra están
          garantizadas!
        </p>
        <p class="text-center text-xs md:text-left">
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@3peso/videos"
            target="_blank"
            class="hover:text-red-500 hover:underline"
          >
            @3peso
          </a> | <a
            href="https://x.com/3pesotv"
            target="_blank"
            class="hover:text-red-500 hover:underline"
          >
            @3pesotv
          </a>
        </p>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-72 md:mx-0">
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@3peso/videos"
            target="_blank"
            class="group relative isolation-auto z-10 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border-2 border-white bg-dark p-2 text-white shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md before:absolute before:-left-full before:-z-10 before:aspect-square before:w-full before:rounded-full before:bg-white before:transition-all before:duration-300 hover:text-dark before:hover:left-0 before:hover:w-full before:hover:scale-150 before:hover:duration-300 lg:font-semibold"
          >
            ¡Disfruta el último video!
            <ArrowUpRight
              className="size-5 rotate-45 justify-end text-gray-50 duration-100 ease-linear group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:text-dark"
            />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mask-gradient {
    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(black 60%, transparent);
    mask-image: linear-gradient(black 60%, transparent);
  }
</style>
